'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. A group of teenagers discovers an abandoned underground train station beneath their city, uncovering mysteries connected to disappearances dating back decades. Their investigation slowly begins changing reality around them.',
'Young Adult',
'/static/uploads/ya_book2.jpg',
'2026-04-03 10:15:00'
),

(
'The Summer We Stopped Time',
'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. During one unforgettable summer, four friends attempt to hold onto childhood as graduation approaches. Hidden fears, fractured friendships, and first love reshape their futures forever.',
'Young Adult',
'/static/uploads/ya_book3.jpg',
'2026-03-30 15:50:00'
),

-- =========================
