'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. A curious young boy inherits a magical lantern capable of revealing forgotten memories hidden throughout his village. As strange shadows emerge at night, he must uncover the truth behind an ancient legend.',
'Middle Grade',
'/static/uploads/middlegrade_book2.jpg',
'2026-03-28 09:20:00'
),

(
'Mapmakers of Alder Creek',
'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Three friends stumble upon a living map that changes every night, guiding them toward hidden locations, puzzles, and long-lost secrets buried beneath their quiet town.',
'Middle Grade',
